*** STAR TREK: DECAYING ORBIT ***


YOU AWAKEN ALONE ON THE BRIDGE OF THE
U.S.S. ENTERPRISE. RED LIGHTS FLASH.
THE SHIP SHUDDERS.


COMPUTER: WARNING - STABLE ORBIT LOST
COMPUTER: ENGINES OFFLINE
COMPUTER: ORBITAL DECAY IN PROGRESS


RESTORE ENGINE POWER BEFORE THE SHIP
BURNS UP. PICK 8 FOR HELP.


----------------------------------------
TURNS LEFT 30


BRIDGE
THE BRIDGE IS DESERTED. THE MAIN
VIEWSCREEN SHOWS A PLANET GROWING
LARGER. A DAMAGED CONSOLE SPARKS.
THE TURBOLIFT DOORS STAND OPEN.
A PHASER LIES UNDER THE CAPTAIN'S CHAIR.
EXITS: 2=TURBOLIFT


1=LOOK 2=INV  3=GO    4=TAKE
5=USE  6=THROW 7=FIRE 8=HELP 0=QUIT
